## WordPress.com Stats
## ===================
##
target 'WordPressComStatsiOS' do
    project 'WordPressComStatsiOS/WordPressComStatsiOS.xcodeproj'

    shared_with_all_pods
    shared_with_networking_pods

    ## Automattic libraries
    ## ====================
